  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ ducks you can grab</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >special events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >relaxing music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 hoop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >day and night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 UFO</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing VR environment where you experience life as a duckhouse keeper*, <i>Placid Plastic Duck VR</i> is a calming experiment designed to induce peace and bliss. You're in for a reinvigorating stay at your favorite seaside pool — now in virtual reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(*Only in VR can you move the ducks!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Placid Plastic Duck VR</i> includes ducks from the original <strong>Placid Plastic Duck Simulator</strong> and <strong>all</strong> the ducks from the DLCs:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducks, Please</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duck Addiction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So Many Ducks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duck Galore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plus, the special ducks from the OG pool!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing VR environment where you experience life as a duckhouse keeper*, <i>Placid Plastic Duck VR</i> is a calming experiment designed to induce peace and bliss. You're in for a reinvigorating stay at your favorite seaside pool — now in virtual reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(*Only in VR can you move the ducks!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Placid Plastic Duck VR</i> includes ducks from the original <strong>Placid Plastic Duck Simulator</strong> and <strong>all</strong> the ducks from the DLCs:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ducks, Please</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duck Addiction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So Many Ducks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duck Galore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plus, the special ducks from the OG pool!</p>",
